graph TD
    %% Professional, modern styling
    classDef default fill:#f9fafb,stroke:#d1d5db,stroke-width:1px,color:#374151,rx:4,ry:4;
    classDef actor fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#9ca3af,stroke-width:1px,color:#1f2937;
    classDef system fill:#eff6ff,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#1e3a8a;
    classDef data fill:#fefce8,stroke:#eab308,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#854d0e;
    classDef external fill:#fef2f2,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:1px,color:#991b1b;
    classDef cluster fill:#ffffff,stroke:#e5e7eb,stroke-width:1px,color:#6b7280;

    User([👤 Farmer / User]):::actor
    
    subgraph AppServer [Application Server]
        direction TB
        Client[Flask Web Interface]:::system
        Orchestrator[Orchestrator Agent]:::system
        Client -->|Routes Request Intents| Orchestrator
    end

    User <-->|HTTP / Web UI| Client
    
    subgraph Agents [Agentic Layer]
        direction TB
        Auth[Identity & Intake Agents]:::system
        Agro[Crop & Spatial Planning Agents]:::system
        Diagnostic[Disease & Nutrient Prediction Agents]:::system
        Alerts[Weather & Email Notification Agents]:::system
        
        Auth ~~~ Agro
        Agro ~~~ Diagnostic
        Diagnostic ~~~ Alerts
    end
    
    Orchestrator ==>|Delegates Tasks & Context| Agents
    
    DB[(Fluxbase Database)]:::data
    Agents <==>|Persist/Retrieve State| DB
    
    subgraph ExtServices [External Providers]
        direction TB
        Gemini[Google Gemini API]:::external
        OpenWeather[OpenWeather API]:::external
        MLModel[Local Scikit ML Models]:::external
        SMTP[SMTP Email Server]:::external
        
        Gemini ~~~ OpenWeather
        OpenWeather ~~~ MLModel
        MLModel ~~~ SMTP
    end
    
    Agents -.->|APIs / Inference| ExtServices
